{"id": 617, "genre": 1001, "title": "为了治拖延，你都干过什么事？", "description": "我认真起来连自己都害怕！并且顶多能撑5个小时！", "record_count": 5286, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606145039gYF1TkIlXCBVOZqK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-07T01:16:17Z", "options": [{"id": 23296, "content": "都拖延很多事情  明天又拖后天  直到最后一天⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268375}, {"id": 23552, "content": "想一想被你拖的那件事儿 是单纯的一件你不喜欢的事 还是为了达成一个目标出现的一点小困难 而你只是看到了困难而不是目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292918}, {"id": 23041, "content": "我覺得我已經沒救了", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174091}, {"id": 23042, "content": "每天看高大上知乎打鸡血，想着今天必须改变，成为知乎答友那般高大上！然后一天就过去了鹅～", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289636}, {"id": 24067, "content": "曾经，注销了人人帐号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206602}, {"id": 24074, "content": "遠離Wi-Fi，就沒有拖延", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265345}, {"id": 23312, "content": "买好吃的糕点激励自己早起 [太有效] 在小本本上写要做的事 做完划掉[作为一位强迫症患者 竟容忍了一页下来毫无作为的情形] ?说到底还是自我堕落", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291740}, {"id": 23313, "content": "唯一成功过的是：买好吃的糕点激励自己早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291740}, {"id": 23060, "content": "卸掉 好奇心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221440}, {"id": 23319, "content": "拖延计划 拖延找工作 不想去上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291766}, {"id": 23575, "content": "等下再留意", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255821}, {"id": 23576, "content": "等下再留言", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255821}, {"id": 26906, "content": "可以尝试自我催眠，对我来说好像没什么用", "image": null, "praise_coun